reviewText: 'Through the Forest 2' is full of gorgeous paths moving through the forest, birds chirping, and the feeling that you are actually there in person. The DVD is beautifully done and would also work well as a non-distracting background for reading or working.I used it while on my spinning bike and enjoyed it very much for a lighter workout. I needed it because I had just finished a tough workout and wanted to slow myself down a bit. I also wanted to enjoy the scenery a few minutes before I got back to work. It would not be my choice for an intensive workout, but would be ideal as a walking or jogging background or as a cooldown after a heavier workout.The thing I like about  it most is the fact that it's possible to visit a gorgeous forest any time you want, day or night, in the heat of Summer or during a blizzard.
summary: Beautiful Virtual Environment For Walking or Running---If You Are Motivated

reviewText: Need to block out the hustle and bustle of the work day, this will do it. The walk is a little slow like the other vids but provides a nice deep green view of the forest. Not very stimulating but will be relaxing. I alternate it out with several others to maintain interest. Kind of boring on its own.

reviewText: I absolutely love this DVD.  I live in a mildly nature deprived area. I love to hike in forested areas and don't really have that here.  It is a pleasure to jump on the trampoline or use the treadmill while imagining myself, via this fantastic DVD, in a forest surrounded by bird's chirping. The only things missing are the feel of the breeze on my face and the smell of the trees and nature.
Title: N/A

reviewText: A BEAUTIFUL JOURNEY..I am lost in the wilderness, and enjoying every moment of it. Im traveling along a road thats paved in a deep gold color by the sunlight. I am very delighted to be here, and marvel at my wonderful surroundings. Trees and Bush are all around me. I hear the call of birds too, it fills the air. And there are many pretty butterflies following me. I have truely gone back to nature, all this has made me happy and feeling very relaxed. This journey im takeing along the Forest Road, is showing me wonderful places, there is beauty all around, this is what dreams are made of. Make this journey, and you will find calm and tranquillity for a little while too. Im lucky to have this DVD, and to be able to have this peaceful experience.  It has left me refreshed. And with a feeling of haveing BEEN there. [Fitness journey through the Forest 2.] Is a brisk walking Pace. [Fitness journey through the forest 1.] Is a normal Walking Pace.
